import { Card, Container, Grid, Input, TextField } from "@mui/material";

function SignIn() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Grid
        container
        minHeight="100vh"
        justifyContent="center"
        alignItems="center"
      >
        <Card>
          <Grid container padding={2}>
            <Grid>로그인</Grid>
            <Grid>
              <Input placeholder="이메일" />
            </Grid>
            <Grid>
              <Input placeholder="비밀번호" />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default SignIn;
